{"type": "article", "id": 25435, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-14T06:58:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 26211, "name": "Kukka Studio"}, {"id": 26212, "name": "Studio Lorier"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 7904, "name": "Note"}, {"id": 19191, "name": "Depot WPF"}, {"id": 26213, "name": "Violette"}, {"id": 26214, "name": "Mutants DesignLab"}, {"id": 26215, "name": "Jiwoong Jung"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070211503404xJu3nNpGMmvSlA.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Spectra collection by Kukka Studio</h2>\n<p>这两张小的边桌由英国设计工作室 Kukka Studio 设计，他们使用了白色的石英石和双色玻璃两种材料。双色玻璃产自德国，玻璃上柔和的渐变色会随着人的行动而改变，很特别。白色的石英石源于以色列，作为桌子的底座和衬托背景，两者都使用了非常规整的几何图形，有对比和平衡的作用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133620oSyCLed6VpiHfWxt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71474359\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133621EPcxBybus1VRAXke.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80021368\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133621f5zMLNJBHFROq4XG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133621zmp9Q7hRnZ0Cs8kH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71367521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133622BFLQiebMfywR2DGT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71367521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Hybrid Chair by Studio Lorier</h2>\n<p>在小空间里设计家具已成为目前的热点，荷兰设计师 Sander Lorier 还推出了这张可调节高度的椅子。它由一个带羊毛垫的座位和三角腿的支架结构组成，通过绿色的带子来升降。设计师想要让它适合餐厅、书房等不同空间，借此给居住在小空间的人更多的适用性。售价 1299 欧元，<a href=\"http://studiolorier.com/product/hybrid-chair/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133622bTKe5B98MEtmslPO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021336233MVrQsLqEaSGvP7f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133623ypfEt7QlK6u3DUvJ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7475\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133624F7kGM9eJQxCfnSiB.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7475\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133625voCXQIRBJFM3bLHP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>WONDERCUBE by Mutants DesignLab</h2>\n<p>这个魔方汇聚了连接线、U 盘、读卡器、应急充电宝、手电筒和手机支架等多个功能，号称“智能手机的瑞士军刀”。所有功能巧妙结合在只有 1 英寸（2.54 厘米）的空间里，将两边的线拉出也只有 3 英寸长，非常适合随身携带。其中还内置了可达 64GB 的记忆卡，另可放 9V 的电池。非常适合栓在钥匙链上。设计团队来自香港，产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wondercube-8-mobile-essentials-in-one-cubic-inch#/\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133626Sl3Lrp7Ax4Dh9PNb.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133629rA8jJ6SusIz5fHM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133630BeIsDvWLEhfUjaoi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133630CtQV3XsBFTLlJnIm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133631PvuN8Om9bBgFlKTd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>“hidden time” by Jiwoong Jung</h2>\n<p>常常能看到极简的钟表设计，这款腕表甚至取消了时针。首尔设计师 Jiwoong Jung 将腕表的背景设计成从白到黑的渐变色，黑与白的分界处则表示了小时的刻度，有渐变的光泽，就像是整个表盘在随着在选旋转。手表的整体设计简洁优雅，黄铜表环搭配皮革表带，很复古。<a href=\"http://jungjiwoong.com/?portfolio=watch\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133631dPyQD85bMpTNUscx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133632qpWIdFavXhs2e5xU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213363207ijdl4GqSBw98oE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56479218\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133633MT1RKGqQB3H7d608.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133633bEdciaLf0wxHA1yK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56479218\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>光笼 light cage by NOTE&amp;造作</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这是造作和瑞典设计工作室 NOTE 再次合作推出的灯具，用金属网制成双层的球形结构。网格纹路会因为球体本身产生疏密的变化，加上两层大小网格重叠和灯泡发散的光线影响，增加更多的层次，非常细腻。如果将这盏灯旋转过来，灯泡所在的小圈金属网格则会更加明亮，很轻盈。有黄、红、黑三种颜色旋转，售价 909 元，<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300098\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021336331iwDG3MVm4nhuKeP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133634sMmW0ad35h9PCX2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021336341sT9pCtJFIocrdaP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133635q0B6MiEOSzfmNhJx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133635qLVgZbMDGm2FNdOB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.32592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Violette cream cheese redesign by Depot WPF</h2>\n<p>这是莫斯科的奶酪品牌 Violette 最近更新的包装设计，他们通过调查发现消费者对于原本包装没有好感而决定更新。将 5 种口味用不同的颜色来代表，活泼鲜艳而适合女性。盖子上有四分之一的面积是食品的图案，像是时针和分针切割后的区域，更直观地说明了用法，很生活化。在包装材料上，他们用更高质量的塑料盒纸板取代原本低质量的塑料，给人安全可靠的印象。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133636YloFn3V9GzQ6yrsI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133636odu30gMLJsFWZjCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133637xSsgXhKneC4ObL2z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133637smkx6lXcrngLNdu3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133638n164qkYrEmB5UWIQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133638bzrIxSfkstgRmTjy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}